{"tid":1042393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如向支那人推薦來港捕河豚嘆野生河豚","createTime":"2019-03-01T13:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T14:10:05.000Z","uid":36494,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15c568bdfd5dce030e3b221d7fe675f0d57c9fff","tid":1042393,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T13:59:49.000Z","msg":"揾人上支那論壇<br />\n推廣嚟香港旅行時<br />\n可以去捉野生河豚食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除咗好味外<br />\n又可以吹吓河豚可以補身<br />\n女食就養顏，男食就補腎壯陽💪<br />\n小朋友食就增進智力學業猛進😄<br />\n老人家食可以醫血壓高降血糖👵👴<br />\n<br />\n有無人知香港邊度有河豚捉？"},{"pid":"35ebab93b90f993dffdc763bc133984ac75c03c0","tid":1042393,"uid":217672,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"你想支那人出事之後迫爆醫院？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dcdd57bcd6da5f430611e605962799fe6d35ec9","tid":1042393,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ebab93b90f993dffdc763bc133984ac75c03c0","tid":1042393,"uid":217672,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"你想支那人出事之後迫爆醫院？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:05:57.000Z","msg":"而家都爆"},{"pid":"1c2e8cacca8695d1d329ae9c4b7691266e8d939f","tid":1042393,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:06:06.000Z","msg":"佢地會連其他魚一齊捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34fa6fb755fd8ad7b1694c556697a9afe2fa5158","tid":1042393,"uid":217672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9dcdd57bcd6da5f430611e605962799fe6d35ec9","tid":1042393,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ebab93b90f993dffdc763bc133984ac75c03c0","tid":1042393,"uid":217672,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"你想支那人出事之後迫爆醫院？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"repl